Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.96,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}I left my bitter street
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:05.13,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Pass the park and bench
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:08.13,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Where we no longer meet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.39,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}I found a path forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.40,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Green and overgrown
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.59,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}I followed my own footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:21.75,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}I walked there on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:28.31,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Threads
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:35.09,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Something's pulling me, I move ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.99,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Threads
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:47.60,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}What is holding is also being held
